#- §lLarge band of raiders caught by Icenia

§0§oQuantonBiscuit, who witnessed these events firsthand, was interviewed for additional information for this article.

§0Starting approximately on the 18th of March
2021, Icenia was
#- assailed by a band of raiders that, according the ChrisChrispie, came “primarily from New Vegas on CivUniverse, and presumably, other PvP servers'', notably including EZ2Clutch, zRoyalty and chosentwice. While the president stressed that Icenia was still mostly safe to visit,
#- both Icenian forces and other exterior forces had been fiercely battling the raiders for days. 

§nInitial Battles
§r
It started when an Icenian known as binchymonkey was pearled by zRoyalty and chosentwice while binchymonkey was
#- giving them a tour of Icenia City. Very rapidly, pvpers from Icenia, the Entente, the UDF as well as Mir logged on and chased the two raiders into Varkonia and Gabon, eventually finding binchymonkey’s pearl abandoned in a barrel.

#- -------------------
        AD SPACE
-------------------




         §0§l方形斑点 




--------------------------------
#- The next day, two other raiders, Ez2Clutch and Toxicity, pearled Naglafer and acquired protection armor in the process, before being joined by the two other mentioned raiders, chosentwice and zRoyalty. The raider threat was taken very seriously, and fortifications
#- to Icenia City were made after the battles.
The raiders returned the day after to break into houses and steal valuables, but were chased out of the city and zRoyalty was pearled.

#- §r§r
§nNew accounts log on§r

On the fourth day of the raids, many new accounts, who were later discovered to be banned players using VPNs, began appearing to join the raider crew.
The raiders’ bunkers were found and were
quickly by the allied
#- forces, which saw a lengthy fight, and while no one was pearled, the raiders were forced to retreat from the bunker.
The next day, the “Wind Chime” military base, used by the Coalition towards the end of the Infinity War, was attacked by
the raiders. Allied
#- forces quickly took defensive positions and fought a long defensive battle that lasted until both sides needed to go to sleep.

§nEnd of the raiders§r

The sixth day saw some fighting around the Wind Chime and the HJE vault “Best Western”, but the 
#- group of raiders were banned mid-fight due to them willingly working with banned players.
ChrisChrispie later made a reddit post announcing the end of the raider threat. 
While the conclusion may not have involved a grand battle ending in a decisive victory
the banning of the
#- raiders was certainly cathartic. We wish Icenia well and hope they continue to be safe from threats in the future.

#- §lThe Battle of the Hole§r

On the 12th of March 2021, a friendly situation in a large hole in Mount September turned serious as newfriends TheNeonNerd, NEBULANDD and AmandaCC continually
killed each other, egged on by AllenY 
#- and his philosophy of §lK I L L§r.
The continuous killing ceased to become all in good fun when, after AmandaCC pearled TheNeonNerd, releasing him immediately after, the latter killed eight baby slimes that AmandaCC had gathered after killing a big slime. AmandaCC then became
#- and was set on pearling TheNeonNerd, and tracked him down.
After successfully finding and pearling him, AmandaCC stored the pearl in one of her personal chests and proposed a contract to Neon that would stipulate him not
coming close to her house herself under
the threat of a large 
#- fine in exchange for his freedom, however it was refused. Then, Nebula, a friend of Neon, broke into AmandaCC’s house and broke the chest in which Neon’s pearl was stored, freeing him immediately.
After this happened, almost simultaneously, AmandaCC requested a trial against Nebula
#- for property rights infringement and Neon requested a trial against AmandaCC for unlawful pearling.
Nebula pleaded guilty in their case, however, neither side ceded in TheNeonNerd vs AmandaCC, and when it came time for the latter to prove her
innocence she wrote multiple paragraphs
#- worth of a recap regarding the events as well as explaining one by one why were actions were not illegal. After this, both trials were freezed at the request of their respective plaintiffs, and shortly after, both cases were dropped, the trio having come to an out-of-court solution.

#- The so called Ceasefire Agreement 2021 was published in court, and stipulated that no concerned individual would kill, steal from or grief each other’s property, as well as forcing each other to drop all cases they had so far requested against one another.
The terms were
#- enforced under the threat of a 15 diamond fine to any breach of them, in addition to anything a court may order.
This incident ramped up fears of newfriend violence within MtS, even though things calmed down after its conclusion. Ultimately, it was a minor setback
to the construction
#- of the Hole in Mount September, however it was entertaining to watch unfold.

